Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.73,0:00:05.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,I am Hanako
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.56,0:00:07.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,You are my friend
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.82,0:00:09.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,He is a teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.90,0:00:11.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,You are my friend
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.32,0:00:17.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喂 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.79,0:00:26.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.13,0:00:28.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.34,0:00:33.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我沒…幹什麼呀
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——op——
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.90,0:02:12.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,橡皮擦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.19,0:02:17.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這彈簧不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.53,0:02:25.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,只要把它裝進去 嚇人盒子就做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:30.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,給我瞧好了 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.05,0:02:37.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.97,0:02:41.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我打不開文具盒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.34,0:02:43.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,會不會是掉在地上的時候摔壞了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.77,0:02:46.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喂 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.21,0:02:47.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,幫我開一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.98,0:02:50.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:02:58.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 一下子就打開了嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.33,0:03:07.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片 你搞什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.83,0:03:11.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對不起 什麼事也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.39,0:03:26.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片的反應真的很有趣呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.48,0:03:31.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要…要你管
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:37.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.40,0:03:40.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,完全被耍了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.86,0:03:44.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,而且還把我想要做的事給搶先一步…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:50.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,本來高木同學來找我幫忙就很可疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:52.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我竟然沒有察覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:55.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,得想想下一招了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.84,0:04:00.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是要怎麼做才能捉弄到高木同學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:11.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:15.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:17.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,借我橡皮擦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.23,0:04:19.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我忘帶了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:35.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,連橡皮擦都能忘帶 你真笨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:38.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是啊 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:53.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:57.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,傳聞要是在橡皮上寫下喜歡的人的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:05:01.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,當橡皮擦用完的時候兩個人就會兩情相悅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:05.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,還真有那回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:08.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,現在想起來 還真是幼稚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:14.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,幼稚…啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.47,0:05:30.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:47.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,到底怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:56.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,上面什麼也沒寫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.87,0:06:00.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我…才不會做那麼幼稚的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:05.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,呵呵 是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:09.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這是假的 你一定又在捉弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.72,0:06:13.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.89,0:06:14.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我寫了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.27,0:06:16.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我在上面寫了東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:19.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道只是我忘記了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:28.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,快點還給我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:32.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:37.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是這樣的 肯定是別人寫上去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:44.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,明明什麼都沒有寫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.26,0:06:48.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,話說 高木同學不是帶了橡皮擦嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:50.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.18,0:06:52.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:55.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:07:00.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,手忙腳亂的 還挨罵了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.57,0:07:06.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真是的 你好歹注意一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:08.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這是我要說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:12.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,老師 我可以去上廁所嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:13.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:23.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道就沒有什麼能讓高木同學難為情的方法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.26,0:07:29.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:33.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,趁現在在高木同學的橡皮上面隨便寫上某個人的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:36.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,等她從廁所回來 就好好捉弄一下她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.39,0:07:40.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼 要寫誰的名字呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.11,0:07:45.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,橡皮上面已經有字了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.12,0:07:52.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,看到了的話會很糟糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.16,0:07:55.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不過只看一個字的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:07:59.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,Ro？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:02.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是Ro的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:11.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就不是…我的名字了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:17.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,其實我也不是受打擊了什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:34.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.28,0:08:38.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我…我要看了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:43.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣的話 乾脆全看了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.42,0:08:46.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:49.05,Takagisan-huamian,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\move(1044,926,1042,872,0,2487)}看\N走\N廊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:49.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs40}註：日語中「走廊」的第一個字是Ro
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:09:00.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,中 中計了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.73,0:09:09.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片的表情真的很有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.07,0:09:14.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,而且還會按我預料的那樣做出反應
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.37,0:09:21.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,所以我才會忍不住想要捉弄你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:24.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你給我看好了 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:29.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,總有一天 我要捉弄你 讓你出醜的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.88,0:09:31.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我很期待喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.63,0:09:34.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你一定是覺得我辦不到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.67,0:09:35.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.76,0:09:38.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我認真的 你給我等著瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:41.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我覺得是白費功夫喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:44.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你可是讓二分之一的大好機會溜走了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:47.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼 二分之一？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:48.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:50.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:54.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,值日好麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.78,0:10:03.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼非要提早去擦黑板寫日誌不可呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:07.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,值日真是件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:10.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早起的鳥兒有蟲吃果然有道理
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:15.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這不是遊戲廳的代幣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.77,0:10:21.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,值日
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:28.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對了 不如趁這個機會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:31.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,在高木同學的桌子上搞點惡作劇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.28,0:10:35.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,睏意減了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:50.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學已經來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:52.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.76,0:10:59.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒有人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.93,0:11:03.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真奇怪啊 是我看錯了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:08.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 我能感受到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.06,0:11:10.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是高木同學的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.15,0:11:13.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,肯定是藏到哪裡去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.07,0:11:17.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好險 雖然只有一小會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.24,0:11:19.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我竟然放鬆警惕差點哼起小曲來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:22.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她在哪兒 她藏到哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.16,0:11:31.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,天真 太天真了 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:34.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,透過間隙 你的鞋子被我看得一清二楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.34,0:11:39.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你是想趁我上去擦黑板的時候嚇唬我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.22,0:11:41.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不過我可不會上當
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.60,0:11:47.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,值日太麻煩了 我還是不做了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:50.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,黑板就算不擦也不會被發現啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:52.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣啊 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:57.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,陰謀詭計被揭穿了 一定很懊惱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:12:02.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哎呀 真想看看高木同學懊悔的樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.28,0:12:04.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.83,0:12:06.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,暴露自己的鞋子什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.79,0:12:08.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學會犯這種低級錯誤嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:12.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 她不會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:14.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,也就是說那是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:17.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:19.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真不愧是高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:23.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼 本尊藏到哪裡去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.18,0:12:28.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,畢竟是高木同學 她肯定會留在這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.94,0:12:35.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,看上去不像是在走廊上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:37.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼 剩下的就只有…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.65,0:12:44.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊啊 去上廁所吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.74,0:12:48.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,看我嚇你一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.16,0:12:52.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.75,0:12:58.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 不在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.06,0:13:19.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我究竟在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.33,0:13:32.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.33,0:13:35.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,竟然藏在窗簾後面…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.87,0:13:37.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒想到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:45.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這個窗簾有點透 所以剛才的我可都看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:49.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡 一副得意洋洋的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.76,0:13:51.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哎呀 真好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:54.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一想起西片剛才的舉動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.77,0:13:59.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我早起一趟也算是值了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.86,0:14:01.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就為了這種事情早起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.40,0:14:03.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.74,0:14:11.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡的高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.62,0:14:13.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喂 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:23.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你不覺得 兩個人獨處在安靜的教室裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.76,0:14:26.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,會有一種整個世界只有我們兩個人的感覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.18,0:14:32.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是能一直像這樣 沒有人來打擾就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.31,0:14:38.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那個…高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.31,0:14:40.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.44,0:14:44.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道說…對我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:48.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:52.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天天氣真不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.33,0:14:56.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真是的 為什麼美奈一大早的就那麼有精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.91,0:15:00.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼啊 這很普通啊 很普通的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.33,0:15:01.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.84,0:15:03.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不可以啊 早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.55,0:15:06.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是喊累的話 好運會溜走的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.47,0:15:07.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,電視裡面是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.18,0:15:09.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你居然還相信那種東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:11.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那種事情怎麼可能會發生嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:13.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.31,0:15:15.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有活力才好…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.23,0:15:16.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8s}吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.10,0:15:16.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,疼疼疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:18.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好疼啊 早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:20.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,別鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:23.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}好啦好啦 總之你們倆先笑一笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.94,0:15:25.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}來 笑一個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.61,0:15:26.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}來嘛來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.11,0:15:24.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你想說什麼呢 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:28.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.03,0:15:33.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,話說回來 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.78,0:15:35.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,值日呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:37.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我給忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:42.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:46.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,鬼臉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:49.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:50.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}知道知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.09,0:15:53.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我要怎麼做才能贏高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.39,0:15:56.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:15:59.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.48,0:16:01.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,幹什麼呢 盯著鏡子不放
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:02.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,中井
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.48,0:16:05.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,在練習耍帥的姿勢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:07.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼會啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:11.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼 是在做鬼臉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:14.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.53,0:16:15.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.91,0:16:16.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:21.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,話說回來 西片和高木同學關係真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:25.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道說 西片你對高木同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:30.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,想糊弄過去啊 看來是猜中了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.13,0:16:33.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片 你小子肯定是喜歡高木同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:39.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼啊西片 你那表情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.81,0:16:43.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真沒想到 我還有這種才能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.90,0:16:46.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好 那麼開始上課了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:49.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,翻到36頁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.23,0:16:50.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,天助我也
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.40,0:16:54.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,恰好是一旦發火就超級恐怖的田邊老師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.32,0:16:55.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你等著就被我的鬼臉逗笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.03,0:16:58.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,然後被老師臭罵一頓吧 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:09.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 真想早點讓高木同學笑出聲來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.63,0:17:11.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 我要忍住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.05,0:17:16.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,在高木同學為了捉弄我來向我搭話前都要忍住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:19.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,人在打算捉弄別人的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.14,0:17:22.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,自己反而容易放鬆被捉弄的警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.98,0:17:25.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就要捉住那一瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.19,0:17:27.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,來 放馬過來吧高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:29.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,現在我可是渾身都是破綻喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.98,0:17:31.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喂 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.74,0:17:32.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.74,0:17:35.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼啦高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.16,0:17:37.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,接招
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:46.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:52.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:56.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,吵死了 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.72,0:17:58.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.47,0:18:00.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太恐怖了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.64,0:18:04.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:08.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我還以為你要幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.02,0:18:10.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真沒意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:11.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:15.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,想做鬼臉的話 眉毛要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:19.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,然後把臉這樣擠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:21.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:22.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒錯沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.20,0:18:24.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯嗯 感覺不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.83,0:18:27.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,比剛才好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.33,0:18:29.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼說好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.67,0:18:32.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,然後 像鴨子一樣癟嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:38.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,居然被想逗笑的對象指導我怎麼逗人發笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:41.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,莫名地感到屈辱…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.85,0:18:43.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:45.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,只要讓高木同學笑出聲來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.68,0:18:48.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,讓她被老師罵了 我就贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:50.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:54.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,很好 比剛才好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.53,0:18:57.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那你倒是笑一個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.99,0:19:00.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是你的側臉對著我 我肯定會爆笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.95,0:19:03.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好嘞 接招吧高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.97,0:19:19.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:22.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對不起 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.26,0:19:28.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真是的 上課給我認真點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:30.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的很對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:35.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真是的 笑得我肚子疼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.03,0:19:38.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,雖然她的確笑的很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.20,0:19:40.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,又被她擺了一道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.58,0:19:45.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喂 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:54.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是再惹田邊老師生氣就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.59,0:19:58.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,總之這節課不能再被高木同學捉弄了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.81,0:20:16.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,總算是往這邊看了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.07,0:20:29.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,大眼瞪小眼 啊噗噗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.07,0:20:29.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs40}にらめっこ是日本的伝統児童遊戯，兩人面對面做鬼臉，先笑者輸。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.07,0:20:29.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs40}玩的時候要唱這首歌，唱到「啊噗噗」的地方就不能露出表情或是做鬼臉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.46,0:20:35.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你那是什麼表情啊 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.25,0:20:38.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片 你這小子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.30,0:20:43.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,每當我對高木同學心動的時候 總沒好事發生
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——ed——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.44,0:22:18.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一百元
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.69,0:22:25.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天也好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.53,0:22:29.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,所以說 不可以把累掛在嘴邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.62,0:22:31.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好運氣會溜掉的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.62,0:22:32.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.55,0:22:45.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.72,0:22:49.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒什麼 你們先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.72,0:22:50.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.55,0:22:52.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我有些累了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.76,0:22:55.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是說好運會溜走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.14,0:22:58.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.69,0:23:02.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,美奈 你腳下藏著什麼東西呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.40,0:23:06.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那個 你們在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.62,0:23:18.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,等等 明明是我發現的一百元
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.17,0:23:21.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真是貪心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.63,0:23:22.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,美奈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.17,0:23:25.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這個是代幣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.42,0:23:30.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為我說了累字 所以變成代幣了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.89,0:23:33.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你還在說那個事情嗎
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——OPJP——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.81,0:00:44.44,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}勘違いされちゃったっていいよ、君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.52,0:00:48.82,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて思ってたって言わないけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.86,0:00:59.16,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}近づく空の香りを隣で感じていたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.58,0:01:08.00,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}校庭で君のことを一番に見つけて今日は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.04,0:01:16.26,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて話しかけようか？ ちょっと考えるの楽しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.30,0:01:19.22,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}風に揺らされるカーテン
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:24.60,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不意打ちに当たる日差し
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.68,0:01:28.48,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}眩しそうな顔を笑ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.73,0:01:32.40,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}照れて伏せちゃうのね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.28,0:01:40.49,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}憂鬱なテストも吹き飛ばせるような
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:48.79,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ねえ、二人で秘密の約束をしたいなって提案です
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.17,0:01:54.21,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}勘違いされちゃったっていいよ、君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.42,0:01:58.18,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて思ってたって言わないけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.22,0:02:08.44,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}近づく空の香りを隣で感じていたいの
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——OPCH——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.81,0:00:44.44,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}會錯意了也沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.52,0:00:48.82,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}和你一起就是幸福 這樣想著卻不告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.86,0:00:59.16,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}瀰漫在周圍的那陣幽香 想在你的身邊靜靜感受
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.58,0:01:08.00,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}在校園的庭院 第一個發現你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.04,0:01:16.26,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}今天要和你說些什麼呢 即便是想著這些也是一種樂趣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.30,0:01:19.22,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}窗簾隨風起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:24.60,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不經意地投入一束陽光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.68,0:01:28.48,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}你那美麗的容顏笑起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.73,0:01:32.40,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}羞得我抬不起頭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.28,0:01:40.49,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}風兒喧囂 似要吹散考試的憂鬱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:48.79,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}吶 我想要和你一起 立下兩人的秘密約定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.17,0:01:54.21,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}會錯意了也沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.42,0:01:58.18,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}和你一起就是幸福 這樣想著卻不告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.22,0:02:08.44,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}瀰漫在周圍的那陣幽香 想在你的身邊靜靜感受
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——EDJP——
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.06,0:20:59.27,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ロマンティック　恋のアンテナは
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:04.99,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}嵐で　何処かへ飛んでいった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:09.49,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}噓でしょう　冷たくあしらった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.49,0:21:12.59,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}こしゃくなえくぼに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.59,0:21:16.50,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ちょっと　心が揺れてる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:27.43,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}本当は本気であたしを叱ってくれる大事な人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.68,0:21:36.14,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて 言いたらアイツは得意気になるから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.60,0:21:39.35,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}もう褒めたりしない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.52,0:21:44.82,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}退屈な運命に　飽き飽きしたね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.07,0:21:51.66,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}知らない言葉で　解き放して　ねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.66,0:21:57.12,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ダーリン　ダーリン　心の　扉を壊してよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.12,0:22:02.92,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}大切のことは目を見て　言って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:08.30,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}あなたとならば　この街を抜け出せる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.30,0:22:14.93,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}今すぐ連れ出して　My Sweet Sweet Darling
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——EDCH——
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.06,0:20:59.27,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}浪漫愛情的天線
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:04.99,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}狂風中不知飛向何方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:09.49,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}怎麼會這樣 對我這麼冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.49,0:21:12.49,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}洋洋自得的酒窩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.49,0:21:16.50,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}稍微 有點心動
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:27.43,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}其實 你是重視我而認真批評我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.68,0:21:36.14,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}如果這樣說的話你一定會洋洋得意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.60,0:21:39.35,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}所以再也不會表揚你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.52,0:21:44.82,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}單調乏味的命運 我早已厭倦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.07,0:21:51.66,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}用未知的言語 解放我 好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.66,0:21:57.12,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}Darling Darling 推倒封印心靈的大門吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.12,0:22:02.92,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}重要的事情就應該親眼見證 親口述說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:08.30,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}只要和你在一起 就能闖出這座小鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.30,0:22:14.93,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}現在就帶我走吧 My Sweet Sweet Darling
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——STAFF——
